1
00:01:58,166 --> 00:01:59,333
[KATO]
Kei! Wait!

2
00:01:59,416 --> 00:02:02,041
[KURONO] I'm so fucking
sick and tired of this!

3
00:02:02,125 --> 00:02:03,000
But Kei...

4
00:02:03,083 --> 00:02:05,125
We don't need to capture it!

5
00:02:05,208 --> 00:02:07,333
All we have to do is kill it!

6
00:02:07,416 --> 00:02:08,541
[KATO]
Yes, that's true, but--

7
00:02:08,625 --> 00:02:10,416
[KISHIMOTO]
Kurono, a-are you sure...?

8
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:12,083
[KURONO]
I'll handle it!

9
00:02:12,166 --> 00:02:15,875
This is the fastest way and we
can't afford to waste any time!

10
00:02:24,833 --> 00:02:27,333
[TOKUGAWA screams]

11
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,250
So are we fucked?

12
00:03:14,333 --> 00:03:16,666
Don't give him ideas, man.

13
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,708
[OKAZAKI chuckles]

14
00:03:22,541 --> 00:03:24,625
I don't know what
these things are,

15
00:03:24,708 --> 00:03:27,333
but they look like big
clay pigeons to me!

16
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:28,833
This is gonna be fun!

17
00:03:28,916 --> 00:03:31,541
[KATO] No! Wait! We need a plan
before you start shooting!

18
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:34,625
Kato! This is so not
the time for that!

19
00:03:36,541 --> 00:03:37,791
Hold on, fat boy!

20
00:03:37,875 --> 00:03:39,333
Like, what's your problem?

21
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:41,458
Look! Just let me handle it.

22
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:46,500
[KURONO]
Okay, you two... Prepare to die!

23
00:03:47,958 --> 00:03:49,583
Be careful, Kei.

24
00:03:54,666 --> 00:03:59,083
♪ So open your heart
up big and be happy... ♪

25
00:03:59,166 --> 00:04:03,083
♪ As you look up at
the big, blue sky... ♪

26
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:08,708
--[singing continues]
--[HOMELESS MAN screaming]

27
00:04:08,791 --> 00:04:09,916
[BOTH]
Huh?

28
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,416
What the hell was that?

29
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:15,208
--[MUROTO] ♪ So listen to... ♪
--[HOMELESS MAN screams]

30
00:04:15,291 --> 00:04:17,541
--♪ That singing voice... ♪
--[HOMELESS MAN screams]

31
00:04:17,625 --> 00:04:22,416
♪ Yeah! And ex-- exercise! ♪

32
00:04:28,166 --> 00:04:29,541
It dodged?!

33
00:04:29,625 --> 00:04:32,333
Those bastards move pretty
fast for something that big.

34
00:04:32,416 --> 00:04:34,166
Kei! Look behind you!

35
00:04:38,166 --> 00:04:39,583
[KAJIURA]
What is that?

36
00:04:39,666 --> 00:04:41,083
You wanna look?

37
00:04:41,166 --> 00:04:43,041
To be honest... No.

38
00:04:43,125 --> 00:04:44,250
[BOTH]
Huh?

39
00:04:44,333 --> 00:04:46,125
[MUROTO]
I spy with my little eye...

40
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:47,583
[MAN whimpers]

41
00:04:47,666 --> 00:04:50,958
Well, he's going that way.
Might as well check it out.

42
00:04:51,041 --> 00:04:52,250
Yeah, why not?

43
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:54,583
[ALL screaming]

44
00:04:57,166 --> 00:04:58,875
[TOKUGAWA screams, grunts]

45
00:04:58,958 --> 00:05:04,875
[ALL screaming, chattering]

46
00:05:08,500 --> 00:05:09,416
[yelps]

47
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:14,041
[screams, whimpers]

48
00:05:17,041 --> 00:05:19,125
M-My daily conduct
must've paid off!

49
00:05:19,208 --> 00:05:21,958
[laughs nervously]

50
00:05:29,041 --> 00:05:30,041
[KISHIMOTO yelps]

51
00:05:30,125 --> 00:05:31,833
[SEI gasps]

52
00:05:31,916 --> 00:05:33,000
[KATO]
Are you all right, Kei?

53
00:05:33,083 --> 00:05:36,125
I-I mean... Kishimoto!

54
00:05:36,208 --> 00:05:37,750
[KURONO]
What did he call her?!

55
00:05:37,833 --> 00:05:40,375
We can't stop moving!
Can you stand up?!

56
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:42,875
[KURONO] That's the first time
he's called her by name...

57
00:05:42,958 --> 00:05:44,250
Either of 'em!

58
00:05:46,416 --> 00:05:48,375
Kato! Get the girls back!

59
00:05:48,458 --> 00:05:49,583
[KATO]
Huh?

60
00:05:49,666 --> 00:05:51,958
I said to get them out
of here! Just do it!

61
00:05:52,041 --> 00:05:53,500
You got it, Kei!

62
00:05:55,875 --> 00:05:58,791
[KURONO]
Goddamnit! Just die!

63
00:06:06,166 --> 00:06:08,791
[TOKUGAWA]
Namu... Shinki...

64
00:06:08,875 --> 00:06:11,000
Please don't let
them come this way!

65
00:06:11,083 --> 00:06:13,750
[STATUES growling]

66
00:06:13,833 --> 00:06:14,958
[TOKUGAWA gasps]

67
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:17,666
That's right... Keep goin'.

68
00:06:20,833 --> 00:06:23,708
[TOKUGAWA] Oh... Namu
Amida... Namu Amida...

69
00:06:23,791 --> 00:06:26,541
--[KONTA groans]
--[TOMAO] We're so dead...

70
00:06:26,625 --> 00:06:28,541
[MIYAFUJI]
I'm not even scratched!

71
00:06:28,625 --> 00:06:30,708
These suits are incredible!

72
00:06:30,791 --> 00:06:34,250
[KURONO groans] Damn! I was
positive I got him that time!

73
00:06:36,666 --> 00:06:38,625
[MIYAFUJI]
Holy shit! Did you do that?!

74
00:06:38,708 --> 00:06:43,083
[OKAZAKI] Woo-hoo! These things
really work! Fuckin' A!

75
00:06:43,166 --> 00:06:46,250
[HOJO] Where's the other one?
Oh, damn! Look!

76
00:06:46,333 --> 00:06:47,333
[KISHIMOTO]
Look out!

77
00:06:47,416 --> 00:06:49,916
[KONTA]
Holy shit! Scratch one priest!

78
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,000
[TOMAO]
Stop praying and start running!

79
00:06:52,083 --> 00:06:54,041
You're gonna get stomped!

80
00:06:54,125 --> 00:06:58,958
Namu... Namu...
Na-Na-Namu... Namu...

81
00:06:59,041 --> 00:07:01,625
It's time, Kato... Please.

82
00:07:07,041 --> 00:07:09,333
We can't hold back.

83
00:07:09,416 --> 00:07:11,000
[KATO]
Kishimoto...

84
00:07:11,083 --> 00:07:15,500
I'm sorry if I've been sending
mixed signals to you...

85
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:18,750
But we've passed the point
where we can hold anything back!

86
00:07:26,333 --> 00:07:27,666
Yeah, you're right.

87
00:07:29,166 --> 00:07:32,583
[KURONO] Maybe we will all
go back together. Shall we?

88
00:07:32,666 --> 00:07:33,875
[KATO]
Yeah!

89
00:07:33,958 --> 00:07:35,208
[TOMAO] Dudes! That priest
is gonna get killed!

90
00:07:35,291 --> 00:07:37,666
[KURONO]
Not if we nail that alien first!

91
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,583
[KATO]
Yeah, let's do it!

92
00:07:39,666 --> 00:07:41,958
Namu Amida! Namu Amida!

93
00:07:45,916 --> 00:07:47,958
[TOKUGAWA]
Namu Amida Butsu!

94
00:07:48,041 --> 00:07:50,833
I-It stopped! Could it be
that reciting scriptures

95
00:07:50,916 --> 00:07:52,708
actually calms them down?

96
00:07:57,375 --> 00:07:59,916
Stop shooting, you stupid fools!

97
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:03,583
I've discovered that reciting
scriptures calms them down!

98
00:08:03,666 --> 00:08:05,166
That's not possible you ass!

99
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:08,083
It's true! For it is written
that with true faith,

100
00:08:08,166 --> 00:08:10,500
one can always find
a way to--! [screams]

101
00:08:15,541 --> 00:08:18,083
[ALL gasp]

102
00:08:18,166 --> 00:08:21,125
Oh, shit! It crushed
him like a fucking bug!

103
00:08:21,208 --> 00:08:24,250
Is that our fate, too?
Is that how we'll go?

104
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:27,375
You know what? I think I
need one of those suits!

105
00:08:27,458 --> 00:08:30,083
Yeah, given the choice between
being dead or looking gay,

106
00:08:30,166 --> 00:08:31,208
I think I'll take the latter!

107
00:08:31,291 --> 00:08:33,000
[OKAZAKI gags]

108
00:08:41,750 --> 00:08:44,541
Everyone in suits, get ready
to attack on my mark!

109
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:47,208
And if you're not in a
suit, get the fuck back!

110
00:08:57,375 --> 00:08:58,375
[KATO gasps]

111
00:08:58,458 --> 00:08:59,208
--[KATO yells]
--[KISHIMOTO screams]

112
00:08:59,291 --> 00:09:02,125
[KATO, MIYAFUJI yelling]

113
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:04,708
No! Kato!

114
00:09:04,791 --> 00:09:06,208
[KURONO]
Aw, shit!

115
00:09:13,833 --> 00:09:14,708
[HOJO]
Damn!

116
00:09:16,083 --> 00:09:17,666
What the hell
are those things?!

117
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:18,875
I don't know!

118
00:09:18,958 --> 00:09:19,916
[HOJO]
Hey!

119
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,291
Here comes the other one!

120
00:09:31,791 --> 00:09:33,250
[KURONO]
Why's he going up there?!

121
00:09:33,333 --> 00:09:35,125
[KONTA]
Shoo! Shoo! Go away!

122
00:09:35,208 --> 00:09:36,833
[TOMAO]
We're in such deep shit!

123
00:09:36,916 --> 00:09:39,541
H-Hey! Y-You guys in the suits!
Can't you do something?!

124
00:09:39,625 --> 00:09:42,458
Damn it! We'll try
to head it off!

125
00:09:48,458 --> 00:09:50,208
[KATO]
Form a circle around him!

126
00:09:50,291 --> 00:09:52,666
Everyone, shoot at his feet!
Try to drive him back!

127
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,250
Sounds good to me!

128
00:09:57,625 --> 00:09:59,083
Fire!

129
00:10:08,458 --> 00:10:10,000
[HOMELESS MAN B whimpers]

130
00:10:10,083 --> 00:10:12,208
What was that?!

131
00:10:12,291 --> 00:10:14,500
Uh... W-What's going on?

132
00:10:14,583 --> 00:10:18,666
[screams]

133
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:21,625
[KAJIURA] Damn! That was
another one, wasn't it?

134
00:10:21,708 --> 00:10:24,000
What is with all the
banging and the booming?

135
00:10:24,083 --> 00:10:26,625
Sounds to me like somebody's
shooting off fireworks.

136
00:10:26,708 --> 00:10:29,541
Man, some guys get
to have all the fun.

137
00:10:29,625 --> 00:10:32,166
And what of our friend, eh?

138
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:34,833
He's not going anywhere. Is he?

139
00:10:34,916 --> 00:10:35,875
[MUROTO]
Nope.

140
00:10:41,625 --> 00:10:43,000
Damn!

141
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:48,166
Keep firing! And don't stop
until somebody hits it!

142
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:15,291
[HOMELESS MAN B panting]

143
00:11:19,291 --> 00:11:22,958
[gasps, whimpers]

144
00:11:23,041 --> 00:11:26,750
What the hell's going
on here? It's crazy!

145
00:11:36,208 --> 00:11:39,375
How?! How can that
thing move so fast?!

146
00:11:42,583 --> 00:11:45,375
[HOMELESS MAN B yelps, screams]

147
00:11:45,458 --> 00:11:47,708
[HOJO] Look! There's
somebody down there!

148
00:11:47,791 --> 00:11:49,125
What?! Down where?

149
00:11:49,208 --> 00:11:51,708
There! He's right there!

150
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:54,083
[KURONO sighs]
Oh, fuck me sideways!

151
00:11:54,166 --> 00:11:57,208
Those things will crush you!
Get out of there now!

152
00:11:57,291 --> 00:11:59,291
[KISHIMOTO] There's no point
yelling. He can't hear you.

153
00:11:59,375 --> 00:12:00,291
[SEI]
Huh?

154
00:12:00,375 --> 00:12:02,291
Other people can't
see or hear us

155
00:12:02,375 --> 00:12:04,125
as long as the game's
still running.

156
00:12:04,208 --> 00:12:05,208
You're shitting!

157
00:12:05,291 --> 00:12:06,916
It does make it
rather hard to believe

158
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,708
that we're not really
dead, doesn't it?

159
00:12:09,791 --> 00:12:14,000
[HOMELESS MAN B whimper]
Is... it over yet?

160
00:12:14,083 --> 00:12:15,166
[BOTH gasp]

161
00:12:37,833 --> 00:12:39,250
[HOJO]
But what can we do?

162
00:12:39,333 --> 00:12:41,666
They're gonna crush him just
like they did the priest...

163
00:12:46,041 --> 00:12:49,166
[KATO] It's like Ken says...
You're already dead.

164
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,125
[SEI]
Huh?

165
00:12:50,208 --> 00:12:51,666
[KISHIMOTO]
What did you say?

166
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:54,000
[KURONO]
We're not dead, damnit!

167
00:12:54,083 --> 00:12:58,416
That's right. And since
we aren't... let's save him!

168
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,500
[KURONO]
Huh?!

169
00:12:59,583 --> 00:13:01,291
[KATO]
With our help, he has a chance!

170
00:13:01,375 --> 00:13:03,416
He's just a goddamn bum!

171
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:07,250
[KATO] We saved him once before.
Why is this any different?

172
00:13:08,458 --> 00:13:11,708
[KURONO]
Shit... We're both damn fools.

173
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:14,125
[SEI] If he can't even
see us, what'll you do?

174
00:13:14,208 --> 00:13:16,750
Shoot behind the statues
and distract them.

175
00:13:16,833 --> 00:13:18,958
Oh, yeah, and just
to make that clear,

176
00:13:19,041 --> 00:13:20,958
since the aliens aren't
attacking right now,

177
00:13:21,041 --> 00:13:22,500
try not to do anything
to provoke them.

178
00:13:22,583 --> 00:13:23,708
[HOJO]
You got it.

179
00:13:25,625 --> 00:13:28,541
[MUROTO]
Ah-hah... There you are.

180
00:13:28,625 --> 00:13:30,916
[KAJIURA] Right.
My turn to do the legwork.

181
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,958
Yeah.

182
00:13:32,041 --> 00:13:33,916
[HOMELESS MAN B whimpers]

183
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,291
[groans]

184
00:13:35,375 --> 00:13:37,708
--[MUROTO laughing]
--[KAJIURA] Did you see that?

185
00:13:37,791 --> 00:13:40,958
Aw, poor guy!
He needs a workout!

186
00:13:41,041 --> 00:13:44,041
But we'll fix that. It's time
for beatin' the homeless

187
00:13:44,125 --> 00:13:46,041
to the oldies. Whoo-hoo!

188
00:13:47,416 --> 00:13:51,458
[MUROTO] ♪ It's the beginning
of a brand new day... ♪

189
00:13:51,541 --> 00:13:55,583
♪ A day filled with hope... ♪

190
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:59,083
♪ So open your heart
up big and be happy... ♪

191
00:13:59,166 --> 00:14:02,583
[KURONO] Why... are they...
singing that song?

192
00:14:02,666 --> 00:14:05,500
[KATO] I don't think it has
anything to do with the Gantz.

193
00:14:05,583 --> 00:14:08,041
I've heard about guys
like this--hobo hunters.

194
00:14:08,125 --> 00:14:09,625
[KURONO]
Oh great!

195
00:14:09,708 --> 00:14:12,541
So, Gantz isn't the only sick
bastard we have to deal with?

196
00:14:12,625 --> 00:14:14,833
Goddamn it! How did
it go after that?!

197
00:14:14,916 --> 00:14:17,166
[MUROTO]
Hell, if I know. Hey...

198
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:20,291
Would you happen to know
what the next lyric is?

199
00:14:20,375 --> 00:14:21,916
[KAJIURA]
Think hard, dirt bag.

200
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,125
'Cause if I can't
finish my number...

201
00:14:24,208 --> 00:14:25,875
...it's really
gonna piss me off!

202
00:14:25,958 --> 00:14:27,500
[HOMELESS MAN B]
I don't know!

203
00:14:27,583 --> 00:14:29,250
You don't know the words, huh?

204
00:14:29,333 --> 00:14:32,208
Well, maybe my little
friend'll jog your memory!

205
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:35,625
Talk about your sick fucks...

206
00:14:35,708 --> 00:14:38,666
If you guys are gonna save
that bum, you'd better move!

207
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:39,916
[HOJO]
So what's your plan?

208
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,250
[MUROTO] Is that supposed
to bend that way?

209
00:14:41,333 --> 00:14:42,958
[MUROTO, KAJIURA laugh]

210
00:14:43,041 --> 00:14:45,875
[KAJIURA] Aww...
It's too early to give up yet!

211
00:14:45,958 --> 00:14:47,500
It was a really big hit...

212
00:14:47,583 --> 00:14:49,916
So maybe another hit
might help you remember.

213
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,500
I'm sorry... [whimpering]

214
00:14:52,583 --> 00:14:55,875
[KAJIURA] C'mon, it must be in
that big thick head somewhere!

215
00:14:57,166 --> 00:14:59,083
Hey, I just got an idea.

216
00:14:59,166 --> 00:15:02,500
Hitting your body's not working,
so let's try your head!

217
00:15:02,583 --> 00:15:04,916
[HOMELESS MAN B] I'm sorry!
Please forgive me! Please!

218
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,166
Don't kill me!

219
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:11,333
Ple... Please, don't
kill me! Don't kill me!

220
00:15:11,416 --> 00:15:13,500
I'm sorry!

221
00:15:13,583 --> 00:15:15,791
[MUROTO] No one's
asking you to apologize.

222
00:15:15,875 --> 00:15:17,875
We're just trying to
make good use of you!

223
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:19,833
[KISHIMOTO] Damn it!
They're going to kill him!

224
00:15:19,916 --> 00:15:21,625
[SEI]
For God's sake, do something!

225
00:15:21,708 --> 00:15:23,166
You heard her! Shoot them, Kato!

226
00:15:23,250 --> 00:15:24,833
Why don't you do it, Kei?!

227
00:15:24,916 --> 00:15:26,333
All right, damnit!

228
00:15:26,416 --> 00:15:28,375
But shoot the bats,
not the humans, okay?

229
00:15:28,458 --> 00:15:30,000
I know, I know!

230
00:15:31,041 --> 00:15:32,750
[KATO]
Damn it, they keep moving them!

231
00:15:32,833 --> 00:15:36,375
Time's up!
Still can't remember, huh?

232
00:15:36,458 --> 00:15:38,375
Looks like it's piñata time!

233
00:15:38,458 --> 00:15:39,708
[HOMELESS MAN B gasps, screams]

234
00:15:39,791 --> 00:15:44,708
[MUROTO laughing]
He's the fastest bum in Tokyo!

235
00:15:44,791 --> 00:15:46,958
Whoo! There he goes!

236
00:15:47,041 --> 00:15:50,750
You know, nobody's gonna
come and save you.

237
00:15:50,833 --> 00:15:53,458
Why don't you just give it up?

238
00:15:53,541 --> 00:15:56,583
So, you wanna finish it up now?

239
00:15:56,666 --> 00:16:00,208
[KAJIURA] Yeah, might as well.
This one's kinda boring anyway.

240
00:16:00,291 --> 00:16:03,166
Oh, don't worry, I'll hit
you so hard and fast

241
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:06,291
that you'll never even know
that your head is gone.

242
00:16:06,375 --> 00:16:09,791
Try to distract them!
Everyone shoot at something!

243
00:16:11,250 --> 00:16:13,333
[KURONO]
Somebody shoot something!

244
00:16:13,416 --> 00:16:14,875
[KATO]
You can shoot, too, you know!

245
00:16:14,958 --> 00:16:16,500
I'm going to!

246
00:16:31,541 --> 00:16:32,166
[ALL]
Huh?

247
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:35,250
[OKAZAKI laughing]

248
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:38,208
Goddamn, I've never seen
such a bunch of pussies!

249
00:16:38,291 --> 00:16:41,875
If no one can see us who cares
if some bum gets killed?

250
00:16:41,958 --> 00:16:44,208
I'm shooting at whatever I want!

251
00:16:44,291 --> 00:16:47,208
--[HOMELESS MAN B whimpering]
--[MUROTO gasps] Huh?!

252
00:16:47,291 --> 00:16:48,791
[laughing]

253
00:16:48,875 --> 00:16:52,666
All I've wanted to do my entire
life is blow shit up like this!

254
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:54,833
Have some more, ya fucktards!

255
00:17:00,041 --> 00:17:01,458
So what was that?

256
00:17:01,541 --> 00:17:04,208
I guess it's the cause of those
noises we've been hearing.

257
00:17:04,291 --> 00:17:05,791
Landmines in a temple?

258
00:17:05,875 --> 00:17:07,541
[MUROTO]
Hmm. It does sound crazy...

259
00:17:07,625 --> 00:17:11,958
But then again, it's still
not our problem, is it?

260
00:17:12,041 --> 00:17:14,916
--[KAJIURA] Whoa! Ho-ho!
--[MUROTO] Whoo-hoo! Yeah!

261
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,541
Check that shit out!
It's blowin' up real good!

262
00:17:17,625 --> 00:17:18,875
[MUROTO]
Eh?

263
00:17:18,958 --> 00:17:21,625
Oh for God's sake!
He's run off again!

264
00:17:21,708 --> 00:17:22,666
[KAJIURA]
Huh?

265
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:25,583
[MUROTO]
Whoops, there he is!

266
00:17:25,666 --> 00:17:27,166
It's still your turn, Old Bean.

267
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:30,625
[KAJIURA] I can't let you finish
the evening ahead of me, can I?

268
00:17:30,708 --> 00:17:31,625
Guess not!

269
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:35,291
[OKAZAKI laughs]

270
00:17:35,375 --> 00:17:36,625
--[KONATA grunts]
--[OKAZAKI groans]

271
00:17:36,708 --> 00:17:40,333
You stupid otaku!
What the hell is your problem?!

272
00:17:40,416 --> 00:17:43,458
Those big things weren't moving
until you started shooting!

273
00:17:43,541 --> 00:17:46,500
[TOMAO] Yeah! If you wanna
shoot something, shoot them!

274
00:17:49,708 --> 00:17:51,541
Where's homeless guy?

275
00:17:51,625 --> 00:17:52,708
He ran away but I don't--

276
00:17:52,791 --> 00:17:54,875
That's good enough,
I guess. Let's go!

277
00:17:54,958 --> 00:17:56,291
We've wasted too much time.

278
00:17:56,375 --> 00:17:57,583
It's do or die now!

279
00:17:57,666 --> 00:17:58,916
[KATO]
Don't phrase it like that!

280
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,958
[KURONO]
Sorry!

281
00:18:04,916 --> 00:18:06,958
Let's try aiming
where they land!

282
00:18:07,041 --> 00:18:07,875
Dibs on the red one!

283
00:18:07,958 --> 00:18:09,416
[KURONO]
You guys hold Greenie!

284
00:18:16,291 --> 00:18:18,750
[OKAZAKI screams]

285
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:22,041
He's coming down!

286
00:18:22,125 --> 00:18:23,875
I've got it!

287
00:18:23,958 --> 00:18:25,000
Try not to miss!

288
00:18:25,083 --> 00:18:26,541
Yeah, same to you!

289
00:18:28,583 --> 00:18:29,541
[KATO]
Now!

290
00:18:32,208 --> 00:18:34,333
[gasps]

291
00:18:34,416 --> 00:18:36,208
[KURONO]
Oh, what the fuck?!

292
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,083
[ALL scream]

293
00:18:49,791 --> 00:18:51,708
This is just unbelievable!

294
00:18:53,958 --> 00:18:55,208
[KATO groans]

295
00:18:58,833 --> 00:19:01,208
[KATO]
This is... insane.

296
00:19:01,291 --> 00:19:03,500
What the hell are these things?

297
00:19:03,583 --> 00:19:06,708
Is there anything they can't do?

298
00:19:06,791 --> 00:19:11,125
There's-- There's no way we can
beat them! There's no way...

299
00:19:13,125 --> 00:19:16,250
[KATO]
I'm sorry, Brother...

300
00:19:16,333 --> 00:19:18,708
I'm sorry...

301
00:19:18,791 --> 00:19:21,583
I tried... but...

302
00:19:21,666 --> 00:19:24,541
...but I can't. I can't!

303
00:19:24,625 --> 00:19:25,666
[groans]

304
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:27,000
Kato!

305
00:19:30,416 --> 00:19:32,291
Say something! Speak to me!

306
00:19:32,375 --> 00:19:33,333
[screams]

307
00:19:35,625 --> 00:19:38,541
You've got to move!
Come on, get up!

308
00:19:42,833 --> 00:19:45,333
[KAJIURA] Here it comes!
Oops, not yet!

309
00:19:45,416 --> 00:19:48,000
Maybe now? It's coming soon!

310
00:19:48,083 --> 00:19:53,041
[KURONO yelling]

311
00:20:17,416 --> 00:20:19,166
[roars]

312
00:20:19,250 --> 00:20:21,458
[HOMELESS MAN B screaming]

313
00:20:21,541 --> 00:20:23,750
--[KAJIURA grunts]
--[MUROTO] Oh! Nice!

314
00:20:23,833 --> 00:20:29,833
[KURONO yelling]

315
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:37,625
--[yelling continues]
--[gunshots]

316
00:20:38,666 --> 00:20:41,958
--[panting]
--[gunshots continue]

317
00:20:44,208 --> 00:20:49,000
[panting]

318
00:20:55,208 --> 00:21:01,583
[KURONO yelling]

319
00:22:46,166 --> 00:22:48,250
[SEI]
Your eyes look so "alive."

320
00:22:48,333 --> 00:22:51,083
I don't know if it's a
good thing or not, but...

321
00:22:51,166 --> 00:22:54,208
...you're so strong that it's
hard to believe you're dead.

322
00:22:54,291 --> 00:22:57,666
And since I guess
I'm dead, too, well...

323
00:22:57,750 --> 00:23:00,291
Next episode, "Welcome Back."

